Next time,
fly First Class or
Ambassador Class on us.
Join TWA's Frequent Flight Bonus Program and
after just one flight, you'll receive a free one-class
upgrade certificate good on any TWA® domestic
flight, valid for six months from date of issue. So,
after receiving your certificate, you can enjoy the
luxury and comfort of First Class or Ambassador
Class® service on your next TWA flight within the
U.S. There's more in store once you've joined the
FFB® program, including:
• Free travel within the continental U.S. at 20,000
miles
• Europe or the Middle East at 35,000 miles
• Free upgrades for TWA Gold and Silver Card
holders*
• Miles that have no expiration date
• 3,000 bonus miles after your first TWA flight as an
FFB member, too.
Join today! For instant enrollment,
call (800) 221-2000 in the U.S.
Outside the U.S., call your local TWA office.
*Upgrades are subject to availability of unreserved
seats. Purchase of a qualifying ticket required.
Please allow 2-3 weeks for delivery of your member-
ship materials, which explain all rules and conditions
for participation in the program. TWA FFB program
rules, special offers, blackout dates, awards and mile-
age levels are subject to change without notice. TWA
reserves the right to terminate the FFB program or
portions thereof at any time.
TWA
FREQUENT FLIGHT BONUS PROGRAM
